commit_list.message:
Linux Driver v160405.

1. TBS5922SE Windows Driver is updated to V1.0.0.5, which fixed sometimes can't lock the channel.
2. tbs5922SE Linux Driver is updated to v160405., which has below updating:
* improve 6909 signal quality
* QAM B support for TBS 6704 (now it can lock both ATSC and QAMB)
* improve compatibility with latest SMiT CAM
* add global version support ( dmesg | grep "TBS version" will return 160331,
i.e. customer can easily check the installed version of the drivers)
* hybrid mode 2 for TBS 6909
* TBS 5926 support for 100Mbps, active by default
* Big changes for Google
* experimental changes for 6903/6908 for EUMETSAT support
3. TBS5922SE Blindscan tool V3.0.1.3 is released.
